Description: energy consumption monitoring agent Scaphandre is a metrology agent dedicated to electric power and energy consumption metrics. The goal of the project is to permit to any company or individual to measure the power consumption of its tech services and get this data in a convenient form, sending it through any monitoring or data analysis toolchain.
Package-List: scaphandre deb utils optional arch=any scaphandre-docs deb doc optional arch=all
